EVP_PKEY_encrypt(3),
EVP_PKEY_decrypt(3),
EVP_PKEY_sign(3),
EVP_PKEY_verify(3),
EVP_PKEY_verify_recover(3),
EVP_PKEY_derive(3) 
EVP_PKEY_keygen(3) 
.SH "HISTORY"
These functions were first added to OpenSSL 1.0.0.

